high_descs: Turn around, turn right, go to the sink
Grab the fork by the sink
Put the fork in the sink on the left, turn on the faucet and wash the fork, take the fork out
Put the fork back in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Wash the fork by the sink, put it back

high_descs: Pick up the fork from the counter.
Put the fork in the sink and turn on the water, turn off the water and pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the fork down on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn around and begin waking towards the fridge, then hang right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the metal fork in front of the kitchen sink.
Place the fork inside the smaller kitchen sink basin that is on the left, then turn on the water to the sink with the fork in it, after a few seconds turn the water off and remove the fork.
Turn around, walk forward briefly, then turn back around and walk up to the kitchen sink on the left.
Place the metal fork back on the kitchen counter in front of the leftmost sink where you found.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork onto the kitchen counter.
